  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Godot的2D角色系统画一个类图。核心想法是CharacterBody2D作为根节点，它应该包含脚本、碰撞体、精灵、动画播放器和摄像机这些组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CharacterBody2D",
        "Script",
        "CollisionShape2D",
        "Sprite2D",
        "AnimationPlayer",
        "Camera2D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，组合关系对吧？CharacterBody2D拥有这些组件。那CollisionShape2D本身需要关联什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CharacterBody2D",
        "CollisionShape2D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，CollisionShape2D要引用一个具体的Shape资源，比如RectangleShape2D或CircleShape2D。另外Sprite2D需要绑定Texture。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CollisionShape2D",
        "Shape",
        "Sprite2D",
        "Texture"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把CharacterBody2D到五个组件的组合关系画出来，加上CollisionShape2D到Shape、Sprite2D到Texture的组合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CharacterBody2D",
        "Script",
        "CollisionShape2D",
        "Sprite2D",
        "AnimationPlayer",
        "Camera2D",
        "Shape",
        "Texture"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，AnimationPlayer和Sprite2D之间还有个依赖关系——动画播放器控制精灵的帧动画，这个应该用普通关联还是组合？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AnimationPlayer",
        "Sprite2D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "普通关联更合适，因为AnimationPlayer不拥有Sprite2D，只是驱动它。另外AnimationPlayer本身应该组合包含Animations资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AnimationPlayer",
        "Sprite2D",
        "Animations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这样结构就完整了。最后确认一下：Camera2D也是直接挂在CharacterBody2D下的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CharacterBody2D",
        "Camera2D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认，所有关系已添加：五个组件组合到CharacterBody2D，Shape组合到CollisionShape2D，Texture组合到Sprite2D，Animations组合到AnimationPlayer，以及Sprite2D和AnimationPlayer之间的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
